          "evidence_text_excerpt": "the Ultimate Package\nThere\u2019s\u00a0no minimum balance\u00a0required\u00a0to open a Scotiabank Ultimate Package.\nYou\u2019re responsible for having enough money in your account to cover any fees, such as your monthly account fee. If your balance is $0 or less, you may be charged additional fees, such as a non-sufficient funds (NSF) fee. Accounts with a balance of $0 or less that remain inactive may be closed.\nEven though you\u00a0don\u2019t\u00a0need to\u00a0maintain\u00a0a minimum balance, you can waive the monthly account fee by holding a minimum balance.\nYou\u2019ll\u00a0pay no monthly account fee by either:\nHolding $6,000 or more in your Ultimate Package every day for the entire month\nHolding a Total Relationship Balance 2 of $100,000 across all eligible accounts every day for the entire month\nHow we calculate your Total Relationship Balance 2\nYour Total Relationship Balance for any day is the sum of daily closing balances in your",
