        {
          "field_name": "eligibility_text",
          "candidate_value": "Effective starting on and after June 22, 2026 (the \u201cEffective Date\u201d), clients who have a Preferred Package account (\u201cAccount\u201d) will receive an annual fee rebate of $40 (\u201cAnnual Fee Rebate\u201d) on one Eligible Card Account where they are the primary cardholder (\u201cEligible Card\u201d), begi",
